description.en:
Kiba is a hybrid of Floki and Shiba - the two biggest community tokens in crypto right now. Kiba aims to spread its love throughout the crypto world by rewarding holders in reflections, and. giving them the ability to utilise its treasury to donate to and action on philanthropic causes.

Kiba is building an ecosystem where KIBA holders get to raise and vote on issues the Kiba community can tackle by implementing a DAO dApp where voting can take place.
